OOC:okie dokie thats all I needed to know sorry bout the delay then.

  Hydras detected new bots outside the base. The base shields went down and 
he exited down the ramp. He was in his robot mode. THe fire flowing from the 
veins of his wings. He had attached a black cape to his back in this form. 
That was definatly a Galvatron choice. "My name is Hydras", he addressed the 
four bots, "What brings you to us?"
